47	tavily_search	superteamdao	Superteam Earn FAQ | The Superteam Handbook\n\n### \n\n How are sponsors selected to list on Superteam Earn?\n\n  Any Solana project can choose to sponsor a bounty or project through Superteam Earn, permissionlessly. If any help is needed to set up the sponsor profile, listing, jamming ideas, etc., reach out to @pratikdholani on Telegram or Twitter.\n\n### \n\n If you want to report a bug or share feedback, please reach out to us at hello@superteamearn.com, and we will get back to you ASAP.\n Superteam Earn is open source, feel free to contribute to our GitHub repo!\n\nPreviousFAQsNextSuperteam Earn\n\nLast updated\n\n Types of Superteam Earn Listings\n Participation Process:\n Rewards/Payouts on Superteam Earn\n Announcements & Notifications:\n XP Allocation\n Policy\n Evaluation\n Sponsor Referrals\n Sponsors\n Miscellaneous [...] What is the process for collecting payments for winners? Superteam / Solana sponsored listings: A lead from Superteam will reach out to the winners with a payment form. Fill in that form and expect to receive the reward within 7 days of submitting the form. Note that the winner needs to complete KYC to receive money for Superteam / Solana-sponsored listings. External Sponsors: Generally, rewards for listings sponsored by external companies (i.e. listings not sponsored by Superteam / Solana) will be paid out to the wallet associated with the winner's Superteam Earn account. Occasionally, some sponsors might ask for invoices, KYC, etc. as per their respective payment processes. [...] The Superteam Handbook\n\n`⌘Ctrl``k`\n\nFor the complete documentation index, see llms.txt. This page is also available as Markdown.\n\n# 💰Superteam Earn FAQ\n\n### Types of Superteam Earn Listings\n\n1. Bounties: A bounty is a competitive task, where everyone participating does the work and the best submission(s) get rewarded. Consider it as a contest where multiple people attempt the same scope of work.\n2. Projects: A Project listing is an ad for hiring a freelancer, where people fill out a custom application form (determined by the sponsor) and the best applicant gets selected to do the work. The scope of work is completed by only the selected applicant(s).\n\n### Participation Process:	https://docs.superteam.fun/the-superteam-handbook/community/faqs/superteam-earn-faq	https://docs.superteam.fun/the-superteam-handbook/community/faqs/superteam-earn-faq	c79d3a33db33177d18f4b52d2b779cb52ec55491aa34f8ae26e5e0c3cfe9afaa	2026-07-01 03:10:53.465184+00
