941	twitter	twitter_suinetwork	Author: SuiNetwork\nTweet: Builders. Institutions. Innovators. All converged at Sui Live. \n\nA clear signal that the architecture for the future of finance, payments, and the agentic web is being built on Sui.\n\nHere are all the updates from the week in Miami: \n\n-  50k+ people joined Sui Live (IRL+ online) to see the future of finance take shape. \n\n-  Sui celebrated 3 years of Mainnet, and the industry poured in to celebrate. Looking forward to many more years of growth together.\n\n- @CMEGroup officially launched $SUI futures. Millions of institutional traders now have direct and regulated access to the ecosystem.\n\n- @RaoulGMI on-stage Sui Live stated that Sui network  provably has the most intelligence-dense, efficient architecture of any blockchain that exists today.\n\n- @paga is integrating $USDsui for direct dollar settlement. One of Africa’s largest payments networks which processed $11B in 2025 is bringing stablecoins to scale on the network.\n\n- @SlushWallet introduced a @Stripe powered on-ramp for $USDsui. Spend IRL, earn onchain.\n\n- @Slushwallet announced the Slush Card that allows users to spend digital assets at 130 million merchants via @RedotPay without needing to sell their crypto.\n\n- @DeepBookonSui launched Predict on testnet. It joins Spot and Margin as a core primitive to expand the possibilities for builders on the shared liquidity layer.\n\n- @warped_games Universe is now live on Epic Games Store. Players can defend planets and own their progress in a game built entirely on the Sui full stack.\n\n- Sui is landing in Reykjavik for @EVE_Frontier Fanfest from May 14 to 16. The game is built to be modded and extended by its players using the Sui stack.\n\n- @guywuolletjr from @a16zcrypto discussed the future of financial systems and how institutional capital is being deployed to support the next generation of builders, at Sui Live.\n\n- @suiballO announced that beta testing is live for their integrated hardware. The first devices will ship in Sept.\n\n- @useLinq hosted a livestream with @EmanAbio to demonstrate how they are meeting stablecoin demand by building seamless fiat on and off ramps across Africa.\n\n- Registrations are open for Sui Overflow 2026. @suidevelopers can compete for a prize pool of  across categories like the Agentic Web and DeFi.\n\nThis week showed the world that the network for the next billion users onchain is Sui.\nSource kind: account	https://x.com/SuiNetwork/status/2052782726575743275	https://x.com/SuiNetwork/status/2052782726575743275	dba2c2f476a1ba138c4ebcadad09bab4c1d8c3a08c11c16d8b780fd18177f8d2	2026-07-03 04:06:41.882485+00
