1190	twitter	twitter_optimism	Author: Optimism\nTweet: Start the week with a quick Superchain recap.\nQuoted tweet: Here’s everything that happened across the Superchain ecosystem this past week.\n\n🏢 @Optimism launched OP Enterprise, a production-grade managed blockchain infrastructure that allows enterprises to own their own chain and their own revenue\n🗳️ The OP Buyback proposal was officially approved by governance. Starting in February, @Optimism will use 50% of Superchain revenue to buy back OP tokens, aligning the token with ecosystem growth\n🥧 According to @growthepie_eth, Over $1M USDC has been settled via the @base commerce payment protocol. \n💿 @StartaleGroup secured a $13M follow-on investment from @Sony Innovation Fund to continue building @soneium as a creator-centric platform for the AI era\n🐙 @inkonchain integrated Flashblocks, enabling 200ms block pre-confirmations. This makes the chain feel 5x faster for payments, DeFi, and gaming\n🖼️ @inkonchain is now live on @opensea. To celebrate, they dropped a free commemorative NFT\n🌊 @nadoHQ Open Beta Season 1 has started. The first structured phase of the program introduces weekly points to reward organic trading activity on Ink\n💰 Kraken launched DeFi Earn, powered by @Veda_labs, @SentoraHQ, and @ChaosLabs. Users can now earn up to 8% APY directly within the Kraken app\n🦄 @Uniswap is bringing Continuous Clearing Auctions (CCA) to the Web App. \n🤖 AI agents are shipping on @base. Autonomous agents like @clawdbotatg and @moltbook are proving that the "Agentic Web" is already live and functional\n✨ @PolynomialFi introduced Yield Markets with @0xfluid. Staked liquidity on Polynomial now earns automated yield even when sitting idle\n🌍 @Lisk published a new deep-dive article exploring why finance must be treated as a core product, not a back-office function, for startups scaling in emerging markets\n☁️ @GoogleCloud launched a new Web3 testnet faucet for @Celo Sepolia. By using @selfxyz for ZK-based Sybil protection, builders can now claim 10x more tokens than regular faucets\n🎙️ @Bankless labeled @Celo "the most underrated chain" in their latest episode, diving into how the network is quietly powering real-world payments and onchain FX at a global scale\n\nDid we miss anything? Comment below 👇\n\nCheck out our website to stay up to date on all things \nSuperchain ⬇️\nSource kind: account	https://x.com/Optimism/status/2018311226363687164	https://x.com/Optimism/status/2018311226363687164	75ffd54a740c5d5796505aa3ac32447d7d2747a37c50842db520ae727581a5fe	2026-07-03 05:06:44.330814+00
