1818	twitter	twitter_ethglobal	Author: ETHGlobal\nTweet: 🫡\nQuoted tweet: 🧑‍💻 Top 3 tips for submitting a strong project at a hackathon:\n\n1. Solve a real problem, not just a cool demo. Make the use case obvious and show why it matters.\n\n2. Ship something that actually works. A clean end-to-end demo beats an overcomplicated idea every time.\n\n3. Make your use of Flare impossible to miss. If you used FTSO, FDC, FAssets, Smart Accounts, or FCC, show exactly how it improved the product and why Flare was the right stack for it.\n\nThe best submissions are clear, functional, and tightly connected to the tech.\nSource kind: account	https://x.com/ETHGlobal/status/2040714442892026284	https://x.com/ETHGlobal/status/2040714442892026284	5eafdb89cf67825fc39b6ed08c87a2ea0cb06808afb4bcdcf295b617855dcbb8	2026-07-03 07:00:17.663554+00
