1920	twitter	twitter_optimism	Author: Optimism\nTweet: Will enterprises fork Aave V3 or integrate V4? https://t.co/7tIRD6cQnL\nQuoted tweet: Aave v4 is a full redesign of the protocol from the ground up. Hubs hold the liquidity and give credit lines to spokes, which control the risk parameters. It also has some very cool features around risk premiums and dynamic configs - all packaged up with super incredible developer docs, SDKs and APIs so you can integrate it with a few lines of code.\n\nAave Pro is our new design take on how we believe DeFi should work. Abstract the right things away and you create a beautiful but still flexible experience. Every single thing built in the Aave Pro UI is built on the public SDKs and APIs which is open for anyone to use. \n\nGo click around, read the docs, and feedback is very welcome. (Aave Pro UI is a developer preview - not the final version!)\nSource kind: account	https://x.com/Optimism/status/1991959894694703406	https://x.com/Optimism/status/1991959894694703406	d310bde41289e6e059b72e1275e931f092157dc28b141271b01f4c37a317ae12	2026-07-03 07:14:25.767383+00
