rd in this case did not match what investors were being told.\n\nThe sector's complexity, combined with hype and unusually high promised returns, can make it easier for scammers to take advantage of people who do not know how to verify the claims being made.	https://www.thecooldown.com/green-business/crypto-founder-guilty-plea-florida-rolexes/	https://www.thecooldown.com/green-business/crypto-founder-guilty-plea-florida-rolexes	15edbea1458ce564411aa47a8c3c13d9f253709c12a913f8e266851222b48164	2026-07-11 13:00:40.75598+00
